data.description: WOW! Great price reduction on this AMAZING home, in an amazing location! Enter through the double doors to this updated home that boasts a great central floor plan. It has an updated eat-in kitchen with granite counters, spacious family room, comfortable dining area, and a large living room that is warmed by the ROARING fireplace. This could be your Forever Home! The primary bedroom has an expanded, updated bathroom, and large walk in closet. Custom sliding glass doors welcome you to the Entertainer's back yard, that boasts a large covered patio, oversized spa, lushly landscaped grassy yard, and mature trees.  The gated front yard has numerous fruit trees. There IS a Tesla charging station AND a Tankless Water Heater and a 'Cool Roof' AND the home is Solar powered!  The home is conveniently close to Northridge Hospital, great restaurants and markets.
